<html>
<head>
<meta name="layout" content="static" />
<meta name="description" content="Rules to make Oddlyeven experience pleasent">
<meta name="keywords" content="oddlyeven etiquettes, carpool etiquettes">

<title>OddlyEven Etiquette</title>
<r:require module="core" />
</head>

<body>
	<section class="white-bg" id="etiquettes">
       <div class="container">

           <!-- SECTION HEADER -->
           <div class="section-header">
               <div class="small-text-medium uppercase colored-text">
                   Do's and Dont's
               </div>
               <h2 class="dark-text"><strong>OddlyEven</strong> Etiquette</h2>
               <div class="colored-line">
               </div>
               <div class="sub-heading">
                  <strong>OddlyEven</strong> is about building a community of socially aware and responsible people who share common concerns, but their sensibilities can be different. We have to keep this in mind when we are sharing both time and space with others on a shared ride
               </div>
           </div>

           <!-- FIRST ROW OF FEATURES -->
           <div class="row">
               <div class="col-md-6 wow fadeInRight" data-wow-duration="1.75s" data-wow-offset="20">

                   <!-- SINGLE FEATURE -->
                   <div class="feature">
                       <div class="icon-container">
                           <span class="fa fa-road colored-text"></span>
                       </div>
                       <div class="description text-left">
                           <h4 class="dark-text">Traffic Rules</h4>
                           <div class="grey-line-short pull-left">
                           </div>
                           <p class="text-left">
                               When we are on to a good thing, let us keep it that way and present your best side. Whether you are driving yourself or sharing a ride with someone, obey traffic rules and drive safely.
                           </p>
                       </div>
                   </div>
                   
                   <!-- SINGLE FEATURE -->
                   <div class="feature">
                       <div class="icon-container">
                           <span class="fa fa-random colored-text"></span>
                       </div>
                       <div class="description text-left">
                           <h4 class="dark-text">Avoid distractions</h4>
                           <div class="grey-line-short pull-left">
                           </div>
                           <p class="text-left">
                               While daily commutes do hold a prospect of striking new friendships, exercise discretion and ensure you or your co-passengers do not distract the driver.
                           </p>
                       </div>
                   </div>

                   <!-- SINGLE FEATURE -->
                   <div class="feature">
                       <div class="icon-container">
                           <span class="fa fa-exclamation-circle colored-text"></span>
                       </div>
                       <div class="description text-left">
                           <h4 class="dark-text">Surprises are not always a good thing</h4>
                           <div class="grey-line-short pull-left">
                           </div>
                           <p class="text-left">
                               Refrain from unplanned stops or detours. Stick to the agreed destination and route. It is paramount for comfort and trust of your co-riders.
                           </p>
                       </div>
                   </div>

                   <!-- SINGLE FEATURE -->
                   <div class="feature">
                       <div class="icon-container">
                           <span class="fa fa-inr colored-text"></span>
                       </div>
                       <div class="description text-left">
                           <h4 class="dark-text">Going Dutch is always a good idea</h4>
                           <div class="grey-line-short pull-left">
                           </div>
                           <p class="text-left">
                               Although the OddlyEven app does suggest an approximate total and shared cost, it is only a suggestion. It is always a good idea to discuss and decide on how to share the travel costs in advance. Most importantly, carry the exact change. 
                           </p>
                       </div>
                   </div>

                   <!-- SINGLE FEATURE -->
                   <div class="feature">
                       <div class="icon-container">
                           <span class="fa fa-clock-o colored-text"></span>
                       </div>
                       <div class="description text-left">
                           <h4 class="dark-text">Be on Time</h4>
                           <div class="grey-line-short pull-left">
                           </div>
                           <p class="text-left">
                               Respect your co-riders’ time and don’t keep them waiting. There is nothing more annoying than a late co-rider.
                           </p>
                       </div>
                   </div>

               </div>

               <div class="col-md-6 wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-duration="1.75s" data-wow-offset="20">
                   <!-- SINGLE FEATURE -->
                   <div class="feature">
                       <div class="icon-container">
                           <span class="fa fa-ban colored-text"></span>
                       </div>
                       <div class="description text-left">
                           <h4 class="dark-text">Avoid Napping</h4>
                           <div class="grey-line-short pull-left">
                           </div>
                           <p class="text-left">
                               Power naps are good, but it’s not a good idea while sharing a ride. It may not be safe (for the driver) and it may not be good manners. If it is really unavoidable, do excuse yourself in advance.
                           </p>
                       </div>
                   </div>

                   <!-- SINGLE FEATURE -->
                   <div class="feature">
                       <div class="icon-container">
                           <span class="fa fa-briefcase colored-text"></span>
                       </div>
                       <div class="description text-left">
                           <h4 class="dark-text">Travel light</h4>
                           <div class="grey-line-short pull-left">
                           </div>
                           <p class="text-left">
                               There is always limited space in the trunk. If you are traveling with luggage, please discuss this with your co-riders beforehand.
                           </p>
                       </div>
                   </div>

                   <!-- SINGLE FEATURE -->
                   <div class="feature">
                       <div class="icon-container">
                           <span class="fa fa-info colored-text"></span>
                       </div>
                       <div class="description text-left">
                           <h4 class="dark-text">Keep your Co-riders informed</h4>
                           <div class="grey-line-short pull-left">
                           </div>
                           <p class="text-left">
                               If you want to modify or cancel your shared ride for the day, plan ahead and inform your other co-riders well in time.
                           </p>
                       </div>
                   </div>

                   <!-- SINGLE FEATURE -->
                   <div class="feature">
                       <div class="icon-container">
                           <span class="fa fa-check-square-o colored-text"></span>
                       </div>
                       <div class="description text-left">
                           <h4 class="dark-text">Always Respond to Requests</h4>
                           <div class="grey-line-short pull-left">
                           </div>
                           <p class="text-left">
                           		For convenience to others, please <strong>Accept</strong> or <strong>Reject</strong> your incoming requests on the app.
                           </p>
                       </div>
                   </div>
                   
                   <!-- SINGLE FEATURE -->
                   <div class="feature">
                       <div class="icon-container">
                           <span class="fa fa-mobile colored-text"></span>
                       </div>
                       <div class="description text-left">
                           <h4 class="dark-text">That call or that song</h4>
                           <div class="grey-line-short pull-left">
                           </div>
                           <p class="text-left">
                               Talking on your mobile or playing music is not a matter of personal choice while sharing a ride. Basic courtesy applies (like in any other setting with people around). Do respect the privacy of your co-riders or ask permission before hitting that ‘Talk’ or ‘Play’ button.
                           </p>
                       </div>
                   </div>

                   <!-- SINGLE FEATURE -->
                   <%--<div class="feature">
                       <div class="icon-container">
                           <span class="icon-ecommerce-money colored-text"></span>
                       </div>
                       <div class="description text-left">
                           <h4 class="dark-text">Currency</h4>
                           <div class="grey-line-short pull-left">
                           </div>
                           <p class="text-left">
                               Driver is just sharing a ride with you. This is not his profession. Please carry <strong>exact currency</strong> to give.
                           </p>
                       </div>
                   </div>
                   
                   --%><!-- SINGLE FEATURE -->
                   <%--<div class="feature">
                       <div class="icon-container">
                           <span class="icon-music-headphones colored-text"></span>
                       </div>
                       <div class="description text-left">
                           <h4 class="dark-text">Music</h4>
                           <div class="grey-line-short pull-left">
                           </div>
                           <p class="text-left">
                               Listening to radio/music while driving is good, but respect other people's taste.
                           </p>
                       </div>
                   </div>

               --%></div>
           </div>
       </div>
   </section>
</body>
</html>